com.sun.jimi.core
Class JimiFactoryManager

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.sun.jimi.core.JimiFactoryManager
public class JimiFactoryManager
extends java.lang.Object

Class for accessing JimiImageFactories. This class attempts to load all factories, and makes appropriate substitutions if some are unavailable. It can handle the absence of VMM, One-Shot, or Stamped factories.
